'''''Ullet''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. It fought at the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], and shortly afterward at the [[Invasion of Bakura]] as part of the [[Bakura task force]].

